detail.name: You Prefer Girls With Short Hair?
detail.effect: [Activate Main] If you have 3 or more cards with 《Satan City》 in their special traits in your Battle Area, draw 3 cards. Then, place 1 card from your hand on top of your deck.

detail.name: 悟飯くんの好み？
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】自分のバトルエリアの特徴《サタンシティ》を持つカードが3枚以上ある場合、カード3枚を引く。その後、自分の手札1枚をデッキの上に置く。
